Our advantages: technical depth, Manufacturing focus, and Jane Jones as a strong champion.

### Next Steps
1. Prepare custom demo addressing We need a support contract to be compliant with our internal IT policies, but the enterprise one is too expensive.
2. Schedule reference call with similar Manufacturing customer
