INSERT INTO sales_demo_app.sales_notes (note_id, order_id, salesperson_id, note_text, note_type, created_at, use_case_mentioned, sentiment, product_name, use_case) VALUES (21906, 5426, 1, '## Meeting Notes: Smith Retail Systems

Extended technical and business discussion with Jane Williams and their team at Smith Retail Systems. This was a pivotal meeting in the evaluation process.

### Call Summary
Productive discussion covering their Troubleshooting requirements. Jane Williams led the conversation with clear priorities around solving We can''t ''reverse engineer'' our existing database to create a visual diagram.. The team was engaged and asked detailed questions about how CodeCraft DevKit supports Quickly diagnose and resolve database issues with an integrated profiler and query analysis tool. Developers can pinpoint slow queries, analyze execution plans, and understand resource contention without needing to leave their development environment, dramatically shortening the debug-loop..

### Next Steps
1. Prepare custom demo addressing We can''t ''reverse engineer'' our existing database to create a visual diagram.
2. Schedule reference call with similar Retail customer
3. Send preliminary pricing and packaging options
